io.github.joblo2213.sma.speedwire.protocol.measuringChannels

Class MeasuringChannel<Q extends javax.measure.Quantity<Q>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.joblo2213.sma.speedwire.protocol.measuringChannels.MeasuringChannel<Q>
  • Type Parameters:
    Q - the physical quantity measured by this channel (e.g. Power, ElectricalCurrent, Frequency, ...)

    public class MeasuringChannel<Q extends javax.measure.Quantity<Q>>
extends Object
    All measured data is divided into channels.
    This class defines the identifier, the description, the unit and the physical quantity of a channel.
